                        <note rend="inline" type="source">825.5151/330: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Philip</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-06-19T13:00:00-04:00">June 19, 1936—1
                                p.m.</date><lb/>[Received 1:05 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>58. My telegram No. 57, June 18, 3 p.m. Delay referred to involves the
                            granting of permits for dollar exchange.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Philip</hi></signed></closer>
